{"name": "fractal-faim-ipa", "metadata": {"name": "fractal-faim-ipa", "version": "0.4.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12"], "home_page": null, "license": "BSD-3-Clause", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["faim-ipa", "fractal-tasks-core", "pydantic", "zarr"], "summary": "Provides Fractal tasks for the MD to OME-Zarr conversion of faim-ipa", "upload_time": 1733408048}, "documentation": ["# fractal-faim-ipa\n\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/fractal-faim-ipa.svg?color=green)](https://github.com/jluethi/fractal-faim-ipa/raw/main/LICENSE)\n[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/fractal-faim-ipa.svg?color=green)](https://pypi.org/project/fractal-faim-ipa)\n[![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/fractal-faim-ipa.svg?color=green)](https://python.org)\n[![CI](https://github.com/jluethi/fractal-faim-ipa/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/jluethi/fractal-faim-ipa/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n\nProvides Fractal tasks for the conversion of Molecular Devices ImageXpress microscope to OME-Zarr.\n\nThe conversion based on the [faim-ipa library](https://github.com/fmi-faim/faim-ipa). This repo also contains some of the test data from the faim-ipa library, as well as test data from the ZMB provided by @fstur.\n\nTo use the MD Converter Task in Fractal, add the package form PyPI to your Fractal server by installing fractal-faim-ipa.\n\n## Development\nYou can install it locally in this way:\n\n```\ngit clone https://github.com/jluethi/fractal-faim-ipa\ncd fractal-faim-ipa\npip install -e .\n```\n\n### Adding tasks to Fractal server\nYou can trigger a manual collection of the tasks:\n1. Create a package wheel: \n```\npip install build\npython -m build\n```\n\nThis wheel is put into the `dist` folder. \n\n2. Collect your package from Fractal web: use the local task collection in fractal web and provide the `/path/to/package/dist/faim-ipa-version-details.whl`\n\nAlternatively, you can collect the task in Fractal via the CLI tool:\n```\nfractal task collect /path/to/package/dist/faim-ipa-version-details.whl\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.dev.task_list", "documentation": ["Fractal Task list for Fractal Helper Tasks."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.dev.task_list.TASK_LIST", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.dev.create_manifest", "documentation": ["Generate JSON schemas for tasks and write them to the Fractal manifest."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.dev.create_manifest.PACKAGE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa", "documentation": ["Provides Fractal tasks for the MD to OME-Zarr conversion of faim-ipa."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.__author__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.__email__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.PackageNotFoundError", "xref": {"fqname": "importlib.metadata.PackageNotFoundError", "project": null}}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.version", "xref": {"fqname": "importlib.metadata.version", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.md_converter_utils", "documentation": ["MD Converter utils."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.md_converter_utils.ModeEnum", "bases": ["Enum"], "methods": [{"name": "fractal_faim_ipa.md_converter_utils.ModeEnum.get_plate_acquisition", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "acquisition_dir", "type": null, "defau